BT 1 0 0 1 0 50 Tm /F1 10 Tf 15 TL (A consistent pattern emerges across regulated industries adopting AI. Organizations invest in governance) Tj T* (frameworks, hire compliance teams, map regulatory requirements, and produce policy documents. Then a) Tj T* (system makes a prediction. An analyst acts on it. A decision is made. And the governance layer has no) Tj T* (structured record of what happened at the decision point.) Tj T* ET
