BT 1 0 0 1 0 50 Tm /F1 10 Tf 15 TL (This pattern was first implemented in the RGDS reference repository \(github.com/mj3b/rgds\), where GitHub) Tj T* (Actions validate every decision log against the schema on every push. The 170+ commit history demonstrates) Tj T* (that schema-validated decision governance is operationally feasible in a CI/CD environment. The same pattern) Tj T* (extends to any pipeline: Jenkins, GitLab CI, Azure DevOps, or custom orchestration.) Tj T* ET
