1 0 0 1 60 79 cm
q
.278431 .333333 .411765 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 80 Tm /F1 10 Tf 15 TL (When AI inference operates at sub-millisecond timescales and agentic systems spawn autonomous) Tj T* (sub-decisions, post-hoc governance becomes physically impossible. The CI/CD integration pattern addresses) Tj T* (this by embedding governance in the pipeline itself. Decision records are produced inline with the decision) Tj T* (event, validated automatically, and logged to an immutable audit store. Human review is triggered by threshold) Tj T* (violations, not by calendar cycles. This creates a governance architecture that scales with the system rather) Tj T* (than bottlenecking it.) Tj T* ET
