BT 1 0 0 1 0 65 Tm /F1 10 Tf 15 TL (For agentic AI systems, where agents spawn sub-agents and interact with external tools autonomously, the) Tj T* (CI/CD pattern extends to runtime governance. Each consequential action by an agent produces a GDR. The) Tj T* (agent's governance covenant \(what it is authorized to decide, what must be escalated\) is enforced as a runtime) Tj T* (constraint. Chain-of-thought logging across inter-agent communications provides the decision provenance that) Tj T* (ARAF's reconstructability principle requires.) Tj T* ET
