BT 1 0 0 1 0 50 Tm 15 TL /F2 10 Tf .043137 .113725 .227451 rg (The decision layer of AI governance is architecturally absent.) Tj /F1 10 Tf ( Existing frameworks govern) Tj T* (organizations \(roles, policies, risk registers\) and systems \(model cards, bias audits, data lineage\). The) Tj T* (individual AI-informed decision, where a specific prediction is evaluated, contextualized, and acted upon by) Tj T* (a specific human, remains ungoverned infrastructure.) Tj T* ET
